{"tid":2415021,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男生管有士巴拿螺絲批 蘇文隆指必用作破壞堵路 判入更生中心 即時拒絕保釋等候上訴","createTime":"2021-02-20T02:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T12:28:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"473cc5a85f0f72249567967680efc97b5812aea5","tid":2415021,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:09:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13806\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13806&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkrHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=940d6091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13806</a><br />\n<br />\n#粉嶺裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#蘇文隆主任裁判官 #判刑<br />\n👤李(19) #1111上水 <br />\n#管有工具作非法用途 #無線電<br />\n<br />\n上回審訊、裁決<br />\n<br />\n控罪(1) 管有適合作非法用途的工具<br />\n（即士巴拿和螺絲批）<br />\n<br />\n控罪(2) 無牌管有無線電通訊器具<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n辯方律師指已向被告解釋報告及他接受報告內容的建議。各報告表示被告不適合勞教，建議更生中心，報告正面，被告品格良好，還押期間表現良好，相信更生中心對被告有阻嚇性，希望法庭能判處更生中心。<br />\n<br />\n法庭在1秒後表示就兩項控罪皆判處被告進入更生中心‼️<br />\n<br />\n辯方表示被告會就定罪上訴，提出保釋期間保釋，法庭1秒後拒絕批准上訴期間保釋。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n按：李手足向旁聽席點頭"},{"pid":"5e6623326e853d0413ca96ead9eec0864898a86d","tid":2415021,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:10:09.000Z","msg":"狗賊"},{"pid":"51a5820e13b0bc9ccda27bd7034d3c1d3d40133a","tid":2415021,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:11:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714b02dd98daca1ac09466f6bad130726a8379c7","tid":2415021,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class